# =============================================================================
# Deep Learning - Training Outputs / Experiments
# =============================================================================
# Training logs & visualization (giữ log text, ignore binary logs)
wandb/
*.wandb
tb_logger/
**/tb_logger/

# Ignore training states/checkpoints instead of whole folders
*.state
*.states
*.optimizer
*.optim
*.ckpt.state
*.pth.tar
*.tar

# Keep checkpoint/pretrained folder structure in git.
# Heavy model/state files inside are already ignored by extension rules above.

# =============================================================================
# Dataset - Ignore large training data, KEEP source code in data/ folders
# =============================================================================
# KHÔNG dùng **/data/ vì sẽ chặn source code (vd: DRCT/drct/data/)
# Chỉ ignore dataset contents cụ thể
**/datasets/**/*.png
**/datasets/**/*.jpg
**/datasets/**/*.jpeg
**/datasets/**/*.bmp
**/datasets/**/*.tiff
**/datasets/**/*.npy
**/datasets/**/*.lmdb
**/datasets/**/*.mdb

# =============================================================================
# Images - Ignore images (keep folder structure with .gitkeep)
# =============================================================================
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.bmp
*.tif
*.tiff
*.webp
*.avif

# Keep placeholder files so empty dirs can be tracked
!**/.gitkeep

# =============================================================================
# Agent Context / Prompt Markdown Files
# =============================================================================
# Các file .md dùng cho agent context, prompt, sketch - KHÔNG push lên
**/*_context.md
**/*_context_v2.md
**/*_sketch.md
**/*_sketch_v2.md
**/*_history_context.md
**/*_Architecture_Analysis.md
review_*.md

# =============================================================================
# Graph / Diagram files (giữ .drawio vì nhẹ)
# =============================================================================
# graph/ folder - giữ lại vì chỉ có .drawio files

